{"tid":366652,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"乜撚野香港獨立，不撚知所謂！","createTime":"2017-08-20T07:45:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-20T08:01:44.000Z","uid":5190,"like":11,"dislike":33,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"af81945a2d0fe40e73a56e8727eae295c66031a5","tid":366652,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T07:45:19.000Z","msg":"打飛機打到傻撚左？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n比你真係爭取到 你搵邊撚個黎做總統呀？<br />\n一獨立 中國派落黎嘅走狗就全部收皮 一夜間要處理幾多野呀？你估自己玩緊sim city呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n成班憤青諗撚埋啲不切實際嘅野 根本就無可能<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n淨係講所以黎自大陸嘅資源一夜斷絕 第日你問邊個攞呀？飲屎水呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所以話呢 有書唔撚讀 係到搞屎棍 你老豆老母真係死唔眼閉 生著個敗家仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/39.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我打埋依篇野就去開工啦 你地慢慢搞你啲垃圾活動 唱完今天我就好準備第二朝起身返工啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/42.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f489f0f79e45af24dd7bfcc8d7ddefe0b9a19af","tid":366652,"uid":6061,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T07:45:50.000Z","msg":"咪踢爆人啦"},{"pid":"f791d611fedc3e70ade6338e59da8bc70f5889d6","tid":366652,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T07:47:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咪踢爆人啦</blockquote><br />\n唔撚屌醒佢地就一日到黑發埋晒啲中二夢架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfc5e46ba0b418183dfc929274b0f105d64ed483","tid":366652,"uid":124292,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T07:47:55.000Z","msg":"聽日要返工，不了，不如唱埋首歌就去食飯？"},{"pid":"2e2d62a5078046e54828116e4e2ce5f7da466e95","tid":366652,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T07:48:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>聽日要返工，不了，不如唱埋首歌就去食飯？</blockquote><br />\n唱完就食宵夜架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ef23a157668ccc3e2f1dbe7263daf3c23715ac8","tid":366652,"uid":85163,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T07:49:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3cb16d6411d65835b0e6818527792cc7e4e88c2b","tid":366652,"uid":124292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T07:49:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>聽日要返工，不了，不如唱埋首歌就去食飯？</blockquote><br />\n唱完就食宵夜架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n都好，趕得切返工"},{"pid":"f202e397640d669946e2dd5a870dd151025fe1ca","tid":366652,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T07:50:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>喂係咪ff下都唔俾先</blockquote><br />\n中二病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19147afc103db7e6ff75b6e1c4654aaae73cb9ce","tid":366652,"uid":130513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T07:51:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"da40afeaf01f7e96c7f237db514e6f1bb7540473","tid":366652,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T07:51:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>天人會守護香港<br />\n糧食危機可以靠國際空運解決</blockquote><br />\n一夜變非洲不是夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64e581595a364e74db6306301404effda69c483e","tid":366652,"uid":85163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T07:59:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"498f8128954cd23e4ef152a127a75d7f56f2de36","tid":366652,"uid":114483,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T08:01:44.000Z","msg":"五毛圍爐區"}]}